snippet.title: Diana and Roma Mystery Wheel of Spaghetti Challenge
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma learn how to have fun and play Spaghetti Challenge. The Mysterious Wheel of Fortune selects the ingredients. The winner is the one whose spaghetti tastes better. Funny food challenge for kids!
Thanks for watching!
